    "title": "Local coding assistant for macOS",
    "usage": "Usage:\n  app start <project-path> [--model <name>] [--provider <name>] [--role <role>] [--task <text>]\n  app model list\n  app tree <project-path> [--depth <n>]\n  app provider list\n  app provider use <name>\n  app provider set-key <name> <key>\n  app provider health\n  app roles list\n  app roles show <role>\n  app roles use <role>\n  app roles current\n  app roles create <name>\n  app roles edit <name>\n  app roles scaffold\n  app project init\n  app project status\n  app project refresh\n  app project summary\n  app memory show <name>\n  app memory rebuild\n  app prompt inspect [--role <role>] [--task <text>]\n  app diff [--task <id-or-slug>]\n  app patch status\n  app patch apply\n  app patch reject\n  app test run [--command <cmd>]\n  app test history [--limit <n>] [--status passed|failed]\n  app test show <run-id>\n  app test detect\n  app test config\n  app server start [--port <n>] [--host <ip>] [--open] [--no-open]\n  app server stop\n  app server status\n  app server config\n  app workspace add [<path>] [--alias <name>] [--tag <tag>] [--pin]\n  app workspace list [--tag <tag>] [--pinned]\n  app workspace switch [<alias>]\n  app workspace status [<alias>]\n  app workspace remove <alias>\n  app workspace rename <alias> <new-alias>\n  app workspace pin|unpin <alias>\n  app workspace tag|untag <alias> <tag>\n  app workspace search <query>\n  app workspace refresh [<alias>]\n  app workspace config [--set key=value]\n  app workspace repair\n  app task create [--title <name>] [--request <text>] [--role <role>] [--model <name>] [--file <path>]\n  app task list\n  app task show <id-or-slug>\n  app task current\n  app task use <id-or-slug>\n  app task plan <id-or-slug>\n  app task note <id-or-slug> [--kind <kind>] [--text <text>]\n  app task history <id-or-slug> [--limit <n>] [--session <id>] [--clear]\n  app task sessions <id-or-slug>\n  app task export <id-or-slug> [--format md|json] [--output <path>]\n  app task continue <id-or-slug>\n  app task 